resources.description: In reaction to the phenomenon that the social demand varies rapidly along with the difficulty in the perfection of e-government system in one step in the course of the construction of E-government in China; the goal of the establishment of flexible e-government system should be achieved by means of the flexible reforms both on the government structure and administration mode.
